Swashbuckler
A game of tourmaline gathering and robot dismanteling

Prerequisites
* java -> http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html
* sbt -> https://github.com/harrah/xsbt/wiki/Getting-Started-Setup

Instructions (in project folder):
1. run "sh generate.sh" in most OS's or "generate.bat" on Windows
2. run "sbt" and type
	a. update
	b. update
	c. run
3. Play!

To generate eclipse project files:
sbt eclipse
Now add your platforms native libraries in eclipse (right click, properties on lwjgl.jar). You will find them under target/scala-X.X.X/resource_managed/main/lwjgl-resources/YOUR-OS

